"636","EXHIBIT ITEM No. 77M: Mergers"
"637","Pursuant to a Plan of Reorganization made by Franklin Managed"
"638","Trust on behalf of its series, Franklin Rising Dividends Fund"
"639","(Rising Dividends Fund) and Franklin Value Investors Trust on"
"640","behalf of its series, Franklin Large Cap Value Fund"
