"1459","in form and substance satisfactory to it, from the law firm of"
"1460","Stradley Ronon Stevens & Young, LLP, counsel to FMT, on behalf of"
"1461","the Acquiring Fund, and FVIT, on behalf of the Target Fund, to the"
"1462","effect that, provided the transaction contemplated hereby is carried"
"1463","out in accordance with the Plan, and the laws of the State of Delaware,"
"1464","and based upon certificates of the officers of FMT, on behalf of the"
"1465","Acquiring Fund, and FVIT, on behalf of the Target Fund, with regard to"
"1466","matters of fact:"
"1467","(1) 	The acquisition by the Acquiring Fund of substantially all of"
"1468","the assets of the Target Fund in exchange solely for the Acquiring"
"1469","Fund Shares followed by the distribution by the Target Fund to its"
"1470","shareholders of the Acquiring Fund Shares in complete liquidation of"
"1471","the Target Fund will qualify as a reorganization within the meaning"
"1472","of Section"
"1473","368(a)(1) of the Code, and the Target Fund and the Acquiring Fund"
"1474","will each be a party to the
reorganization within the meaning of Section 368(b) of the Code;"
"1475","(2) 	No gain or loss will be recognized by the Target Fund upon the"
"1476","transfer of substantially all of its assets to the Acquiring Fund in"
"1477","exchange solely for the Acquiring Fund Shares pursuant to Section"
"1478","361(a) and Section 357(a) of the Code;"
"1479","(3) 	No gain or loss will be recognized by the Acquiring Fund"
"1480","upon the receipt by it of substantially all of the assets of the"
"1481","Target Fund in exchange solely for the Acquiring Fund Shares"
"1482","pursuant to Section 1032(a) of the Code;"
"1483","(4)       No gain or loss will be recognized by the Target Fund"
"1484","upon the distribution of the Acquiring Fund Shares by the Target"
"1485","Fund to its shareholders in complete liquidation pursuant to"
"1486","Section 361(c)(1) of the Code;"
"1487","(5) 	The tax basis of the assets of the Target Fund received"
"1488","by the Acquiring Fund will be the same as the tax basis of these"
"1489","assets in the hands of the Target Fund immediately prior to the"
"1490","Reorganization pursuant to Section 362(b) of the Code;"
"1491","(6) 	The holding periods of the assets of the Target Fund"
"1492","received by the Acquiring Fund will include the periods during"
"1493","which such assets were held by the Target Fund pursuant to"
"1494","Section 1223(2) of the Code;"
"1495","(7) 	No gain or loss will be recognized by the shareholders"
"1496","of the"
"1497","Target Fund upon the exchange of their Target Fund Shares solely"
"1498","for the Acquiring Fund Shares (including fractional shares to"
"1499","which they may be entitled) pursuant to Section 354(a) of the Code;"
"1500","(8) 	The aggregate tax basis of the Acquiring Fund Shares to be"
"1501","received by each Target Fund shareholder (including fractional"
"1502","shares to which they may be"
"1503","entitled) will be the same as the aggregate tax basis of the Target"
"1504","Fund Shares exchanged therefor pursuant to Section 358(a)(l) of"
"1505","the Code;"
"1506","(9) 	The holding period of the Acquiring Fund Shares to be"
"1507","received by each Target Fund shareholder (including fractional"
"1508","shares to which they may be entitled) will include the holding"
"1509","period of the Target Fund Shares surrendered in exchange"
"1510","therefor, provided that the shareholder held the Target Fund"
"1511","Shares as a capital asset on the date of the Reorganization"
"1512","pursuant to Section 1223(1) of the Code;"
"1513","(10) 	The Acquiring Fund will succeed to and take into account"
"1514","as of the date of the transfer (as defined in Section 1.381(b)-l(b)"
"1515","of Treasury Regulations) the items of the Target Fund described in"
"1516","Section 381(c) of the Code, subject to the conditions and"
"1517","limitations specified in Sections 381, 382, 383 and 384 of the"
"1518","Code and the Treasury Regulations"
"1519","thereunder."
"1520","No opinion will be expressed as to the effect of the"
"1521","Reorganization on: (i) the Target Fund or the Acquiring Fund"
"1522","with respect to any asset as to which any unrealized gain or"
"1523","loss is required to be recognized for federal income tax"
"1524","purposes at the end of a taxable year (or on the termination or"
"1525","transfer thereof) under a mark-to-market system of accounting;"
"1526","and (ii) any Target Fund shareholder that is required to recognize"
"1527","unrealized gains and losses for federal income tax purposes under"
"1528","a mark-to-market system of accounting."
"1529","(i) 	That the Acquiring Fund's  Prospectus contained in the"
"1530","Registration Statement with respect to Acquiring Fund Shares to be"
"1531","delivered to Target Fund shareholders in accordance with the Plan"
"1532","shall be effective, and no stop order suspending the effectiveness"
"1533","of the Registration Statement or any amendment or supplement thereto,"
"1534","shall have been issued prior to the Closing Date or shall be in"
"1535","effect at the Closing, and no proceedings for the issuance of such"
"1536","an order shall be pending or threatened on that date."
"1537","G)	That the Acquiring Fund Shares to be delivered hereunder"
"1538","shall be eligible for sale with each state commission or agency"
"1539","with which such eligibility is required in order to permit the"
"1540","Acquiring Fund Shares lawfully to be delivered to each holder of"
"1541","the Target Fund Shares."
