"1563","the Plan may be terminated and the Reorganization abandoned at any time"
"1564","prior (whether before or after approval thereof by the shareholders of"
"1565","the Target Fund) to the Closing, or the Closing may be postponed:"
"1566","(1) 	by mutual consent of FMT, on behalf of the Acquiring Fund, and"
