"1568","(2) 	by FVIT, on behalf of the Target Fund, if any condition of its"
"1569","obligations set forth in Section 6 has not been fulfilled or waived and"
"1570","it reasonably appears that such condition or"
"1571","obligation will not or cannot"
"1572","be met; or"
"1573","(3)       by FMT, on behalf of the Acquiring Fund, if"
"1574","any conditions of its"
"1575","obligations set forth in Section 6 has not been"
"1576","fulfilled or waived and it"
"1577","reasonably appears that such condition or obligation"
"1578","will not or cannot be met."
"1579","(b)       If the transactions contemplated by the Plan have not been"
"1580","consummated by December 31, 2016, the Plan shall automatically"
"1581","terminate on that date, unless a later date is mutually agreed"
