"1593","(d) 	At any time prior to the Closing, any of the"
"1594","terms or conditions of the Plan may be waived by FMT,"
"1595","on behalf of the Acquiring Fund, or FVIT, on behalf of"
"1596","the Target"
"1597","Fund, if, in the judgment of their respective officers,"
"1598","such action or waiver will not have a material adverse"
