"1631","(b) 	Any reporting responsibility of the Target Fund is and shall"
"1632","remain the responsibility of FVIT, up to and including the Closing"
"1633","Date, and such later date on which the Target Fund is terminated"
"1634","including, without limitation, responsibility for (i) preparing and"
"1635","filing Tax Returns relating to Tax periods ending on or prior to the"
